 119:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****     *** MDMA functional mode ***
 120:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****     ====================================
 121:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****     [..]
 122:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****      Configure the SourceInc and DestinationInc of MDMA parameters in the HAL_OSPI_MspInit() functi
 123:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****      (+) MDMA settings for write operation :
 124:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****          (++) The DestinationInc should be MDMA_DEST_INC_DISABLE
 125:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****          (++) The SourceInc must be a value of @ref MDMA_Source_increment_mode (Except the MDMA_SRC
 126:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****          (++) The SourceDataSize must be a value of @ref MDMA Source data size
 127:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****               (Except the MDMA_SRC_DATASIZE_DOUBLEWORD)
 128:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****               aligned with @ref MDMA_Source_increment_mode .
 129:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****          (++) The DestDataSize must be a value of @ref MDMA Destination data size
 130:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****               (Except the MDMA_DEST_DATASIZE_DOUBLEWORD)
 131:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****      (+) MDMA settings for read operation :
 132:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****          (++) The SourceInc should be MDMA_SRC_INC_DISABLE
 133:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****          (++) The DestinationInc must be a value of @ref MDMA_Destination_increment_mode
 134:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****          (Except the MDMA_DEST_INC_DOUBLEWORD).
 135:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****          (++) The SourceDataSize must be a value of @ref MDMA Source data size
 136:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****               (Except the MDMA_SRC_DATASIZE_DOUBLEWORD) .
 137:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****          (++) The DestDataSize must be a value of @ref MDMA Destination data size
 138:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****               (Except the MDMA_DEST_DATASIZE_DOUBLEWORD)
 139:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****               aligned with @ref MDMA_Destination_increment_mode.
 140:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****      (+) The buffer Transfer Length (BufferTransferLength) = number of bytes in the FIFO (FifoThres
 141:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****     [..]
 142:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****      In case of wrong MDMA setting
 143:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****      (+) For write operation :
 144:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****          (++) If the DestinationInc is different to MDMA_DEST_INC_DISABLE , it will be disabled
 145:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****               by the HAL_OSPI_Transmit_DMA().
