 150:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****     *** Memory-mapped functional mode ***
 151:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****     =====================================
 152:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****     [..]
 153:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****      Configure the command sequence by the same way than the indirect mode except
 154:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****      for the operation type in regular mode :
 155:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****      (+) Operation type equals to read configuration : the command configuration
 156:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****          applies to read access in memory-mapped mode
 157:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****      (+) Operation type equals to write configuration : the command configuration
 158:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****          applies to write access in memory-mapped mode
 159:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****      (+) Both read and write configuration should be performed before activating
 160:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****          memory-mapped mode
 161:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****     [..]
 162:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ospi.c ****      Configure the memory-mapped functional mode using the HAL_OSPI_MemoryMapped()
